                                Horizontal scaling<br />
                                <div.subtext>(add more machines)</div>
                                ---
                        tr
                            td - Upgrade and Maintenance Releases
                            td
                                ---
                                Continuous Delivery
                                <div.subtext>(small incremental updates)</div>
                                ---
                        tr
